# =====================================================================
# STM32 vendor code (CMSIS / HAL drivers) -- not our source
# =====================================================================
**/Drivers/CMSIS/
**/Drivers/STM32*_HAL_Driver/

# =====================================================================
# Keil MDK-ARM build output (keep project files: *.uvprojx, *.uvoptx)
# =====================================================================
**/MDK-ARM/**/Objects/
**/MDK-ARM/**/Listings/
**/MDK-ARM/**/RTE/
**/MDK-ARM/**/DebugConfig/
**/MDK-ARM/*.bak
**/MDK-ARM/*.uvguix.*

# =====================================================================
# STM32CubeIDE / GCC / generic build output directories
# =====================================================================
**/Debug/
**/Release/
**/build/
**/Build/
**/Objects/
**/Listings/
**/RTE/

